title: My Queer Experience
description:
In honor of Pride Month, Camo sits down with all of you to talk in-depth about their experience growing up queer in a homophobic environment. Tune in to hear how they overcame the judgement of others and learned to own who they are and inspire others to be more accepting. And don't miss the end of the episode where Camo answers all your juicy fan questions!!
